{"data":[{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"0_1698229369.847331","card_id":"Q_627587141","target":{"id":627587141,"title":"如何看待「李佳琦直播间时隔 43 天再次带货花西子」，这意味着什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/627587141","type":"question","created":1698138996,"answer_count":1092,"follower_count":1529,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[21973,467414,547242],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"10月24日，在此前的79元眉笔事件风波后，李佳琦直播间时隔43天再次直播带货花西子，不过李佳琦本人并未出镜现身为此次花西子产品讲解带货。截至24日12:08，直播间观看人次已超1000万。 此前，9月10日，李佳琦直播介绍79元一支的花西子眉笔时，看到网友留言说贵，回复网友称79元眉笔买不起是不是因为工作不够努力，同时被曝光79元眉笔仅有0.08g比黄金还要贵，导致广大网友认为李佳琦轻视普通人、制造焦虑且虚抬商品价格。 9月11日凌晨，李佳琦发布博文道歉，同日晚间发布道歉视频，称自己言论不当让大家失望，也会反思最初为什么要出发，怎样做能服务好更多女生，再次感谢大家对他的批评和监督。 在79元眉笔事件前，李佳琦微博粉丝数3043.5万，截至10月24日11点，粉丝数2874.7万，掉粉超168万。（梨视频）"},"attached_info":"CkAIhNiBuMX3xYYVEAMaCTEwMTc0MjYzOSD0lt6pBjAAOPkLQAByCTYyNzU4NzE0MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"929 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-58510b6c03a9ec0710c60cdf85a7e4fd_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"1_1698229369.849077","card_id":"Q_546103286","target":{"id":546103286,"title":"如果把一块猪肉放入稀有气体环境中，并每天进行辐照灭菌，那么猪肉会腐烂吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/546103286","type":"question","created":1659158315,"answer_count":97,"follower_count":247,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[361,4075,259795],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IhNiBuMX3xYYVEAMaCDgzNjM5Mjc2IKv+kpcGMAA49wFAAXIJNTQ2MTAzMjg2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"473 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-37fd1725d6b360e3cecc00eefa4b9971_14